Snapchat has launched its new Spectacles camera glasses, which boast an array of new features. The glasses can now take photos in addition to recording video, and Snapchat said its first-generation glasses would receive the ability to take photos in a firmware update. The second-generation Spectacles are also water-resistant and sync with your smartphone at a faster rate. Users can also order the new Spectacles with a pair of prescription lenses through Lensabl. The new Spectacles are priced at $150 and can be ordered from the official website. 